  "回档(后悔药)": "Undo history",
  "对知识树/考试结构的每一次大改(重建、合并、复制、挂父、开汇总等)都自动留了一个还原点。想撤就点「撤销」,把相关考试还原到那次改动之前。默认保留最近 40 次、最多 60 天,更早的自动清掉。": "Every major change to your knowledge tree / exam structure (rebuild, merge, copy, attach, combined-review, etc.) automatically leaves a restore point. Hit Undo to roll the affected exams back to before that change. The latest 40 (up to 60 days) are kept; older ones are auto-cleared.",
  "确定回档撤销这次「{x}」?这会把相关考试还原到该操作【执行前】的状态,当前之后的改动会被覆盖。": "Undo \"{x}\"? This restores the affected exams to their state BEFORE that operation; changes made since will be overwritten.",
