  "正在组卷…题库不够会即时生成,可能要等一会儿。退出之后后台会继续生成,可以过一会回来看看。": "Building the paper… if the bank is short, questions are generated on the fly, so it may take a while. After you leave, generation keeps running in the background — check back in a little while.",
