  "💡 这些都是可选的,不用每项都填——即使标了 🔴 也可以留空/跳过,以后随时补。填得多 AI 更准,但空着也能生成。": "💡 These are all optional — you don't have to fill every item; even 🔴 ones can be left blank/skipped and added later. More detail helps the AI, but it can generate with them empty.",
  "正在联网搜索这门考试的公开信息,并生成 AI 认知自评…(约 2 分钟,可能更久)": "Searching the web for public info on this exam and writing the AI self-assessment… (about 2 minutes, maybe longer)",
