  "把每一场考试当成猎物。这是你的私人 AI 备考助手,先花 20 秒认认路。": "Treat every exam as prey. This is your personal AI study assistant—take 20 seconds to find your way around.",
  "先锁定目标": "Lock your target first",
  "在「追杀计划」里新建考试(选类型;只想学知识、不考试就选「只学习」)。再到「资料」上传大纲/教材/真题,或用浏览器扩展从网页采集——拖拽、粘贴都行。": "Add an exam in “Murder Plan” (pick a type; choose “Study only” if you just want to learn without an exam). Then upload syllabus/textbooks/past papers in “Materials”, or collect from the web with the browser extension—drag & drop or paste too.",
  "学 + 练": "Learn + practice",
  "「学习」看 AI 讲知识点并开始练习,做题即时批改;答错的自动进「错题本」按 1/3/7/15/30 天重练;练习优先用真题/网上题,没有才 AI 出题。": "In “Study”, read AI explanations and start practicing with instant grading; wrong answers go to “Mistakes” for review on a 1/3/7/15/30-day schedule; practice uses real/online questions first, AI-made only as fallback.",
  "问问杀手:你的 AI 助手": "Ask Killer: your AI assistant",
  "有问题直接聊。它什么都能看、也能帮你改(改前会征求你同意),还能指挥浏览器扩展去网站采集。所有对话都能传文件、拖拽或粘贴截图。": "Chat about anything. It can see everything and make changes for you (with your OK first), and can direct the browser extension to collect from sites. Every chat accepts files—drag or paste screenshots.",
  "越用越懂你": "It gets to know you",
  "「你的全部杀技」是跨所有考试的长期画像,每个考试都会读它,做题多了自动更新。想留的题和心得放「笔记本」;「屠杀准备」考前再看;右下角随时能「意见反馈」。": "“All Your Killing Skills” is a long-term profile across all your exams that every exam reads and that auto-updates as you practice. Keep questions and notes in “Notebook”; check “Slaughter Prep” before exam day; “Feedback” is always at the bottom-right.",
  "让 AI 更新你的全部杀技": "Let AI update your killing skills",
  "这套杀技档案还是空的。点「让 AI 更新」根据你的做题情况自动生成,或点「编辑」自己写。": "No killing skills on file yet. Tap “Let AI update” to auto-generate from your practice, or “Edit” to write your own.",
