  "点色=掌握度(绿=掌握/浅绿=一般/红=薄弱/灰=未学);🟢🟡⚪=资料覆盖。点知识点看讲解。": "Dot = mastery (green=mastered / light=ok / red=weak / grey=new); 🟢🟡⚪ = material coverage. Tap a topic for the lesson.",
  "反馈:题目有问题": "Report: question is flawed",
  "如果是答案或解析你不认同,建议直接用上面的“追问/争论”和 AI 讨论。这里只反馈“题目本身”的毛病(如题干歧义、无正确选项、需要图/音频等)。": "If you disagree with the answer/explanation, use “Ask/dispute” above to discuss with the AI. This is only for flaws in the question itself (ambiguous stem, no correct option, needs image/audio, etc.).",
  "补充说明(可选):这题哪里有问题?写清楚能帮 AI 更准地改进": "Note (optional): what's wrong with it? Details help the AI improve.",
  "提交后 AI 会分析错因,据此改进题库和以后出题。若分析不出问题且你没补充说明,则当误操作、不删题。": "After you submit, the AI analyzes the cause and improves the bank & future generation. If it finds nothing and you left no note, it's treated as a misclick — the question isn't removed.",
  "取消": "Cancel",
  "提交": "Submit",
  "AI 确认这题确有问题,已移除并改进出题。感谢!": "AI confirmed the flaw, removed it, and improved future questions. Thanks!",
  "AI 没发现这题有明显问题,已忽略(未删除)。若确有问题,请补充说明再提交。": "AI found no clear flaw, so it was ignored (not removed). If there is one, add a note and resubmit.",
  "直接回答": "answer directly",
  "上传文件": "upload file",
  "更多": "More",
  "更多功能": "More features",
  "语言/档案/导出": "Language / profile / export",
  "使用情况/子账号": "Usage / sub-accounts",
  "调试": "Debug",
  "讨论中沉淀的观察": "Insights from discussions",
  "已据此更新熟悉程度:": "Mastery updated: ",
  "嘲讽已送出!": "Taunt sent!",
  "📬 欢迎使用 Kill Your Exam": "📬 Welcome to Kill Your Exam",
  "把每一场考试当成猎物。这里是你的私人 AI 备考助手——上传资料、AI 讲知识点出练习题、盯进度排计划。有任何更新,都会像信件一样出现在这个收件箱里,看完可以删掉。祝你旗开得胜。\n\n——开发者 Will": "Treat every exam like prey. This is your personal AI study coach — upload your materials, and the AI explains topics, generates practice, tracks progress and plans your prep. Any updates show up here in your inbox like letters; delete them once read. Good luck out there.\n\n— Will, the developer",
  "✨ 新功能更新": "✨ What's New",
  "排行榜 + 嘲讽大战": "Leaderboard + taunt wars",
  "主页新增做题排行榜(本周榜 / 总榜)。周榜或总榜榜一可以对任意人发出「嘲讽」;被嘲讽的人能回一记「不屑」,榜一还能再嘲讽回去——快去卷,别被人骑脸。": "The home page now has a practice leaderboard (this week / all-time). Whoever is #1 on the weekly or all-time board can \"taunt\" anyone ranked below; the taunted person can fire back a \"scoff\", and the champion can taunt again — so grind, or get owned.",
  "消息提醒": "Notifications",
  "在「设置」里开启后,可以像聊天软件一样收到推送提醒(更新公告、Bug 回复、排名嘲讽)。三个开关各自独立;无论怎么设,收件箱始终照收更新和 Bug 回复。": "Turn it on in Settings to get chat-app-style push reminders (update announcements, bug replies, ranking taunts). The three toggles are independent; either way, your inbox always receives updates and bug replies.",
  "一键反馈 Bug": "One-tap bug reports",
  "做题时遇到功能或设计问题(比如录不了音、题目与选项错乱),点「反馈bug」,就能把整道题连同你的作答、草稿、录音一起发给开发者,修得更快。": "Hit a functional or design issue while practicing (e.g. recording won't work, question and options mismatched)? Tap \"Report a bug\" to send the whole question — plus your answer, scratchpad and recording — to the developer, so it gets fixed faster.",
  "模拟考全面升级": "Mock exams, upgraded",
  "现在先由 AI 规划这门考试的「蓝图」(考哪些知识点、各出几题、多少分)再组卷,题库不够会即时出题;交卷后能逐题回顾、按分值计分,记录永久保存,还能对每道题追问争论。": "The mock exam now first has the AI plan a \"blueprint\" (which topics, how many questions each, total marks) and builds the paper from it, generating questions on the fly if the bank is short; after submitting you can review each question, get marks-based scoring, keep the record forever, and even argue any question.",
  "多语言": "Multiple languages",
  "界面支持简体 / 英文 / 繁体(台湾·港澳)等多种语言,可在「设置」里随时切换。": "The interface supports multiple languages — Simplified Chinese, English, Traditional Chinese (Taiwan / HK-Macau) and more — switch anytime in Settings.",
