  "✓ 已保存": "✓ Saved",
  "「学习」在首页「更多功能」里,看 AI 讲知识点并开始练习,做题即时批改;答错的自动进「错题本」按 1/3/7/15/30 天重练;练习优先用真题/网上题,没有才 AI 出题。": "\"Study\" is under \"More\" on the home page: the AI explains topics and you start practicing with instant grading; wrong answers go into the Mistakes book and are re-practiced on a 1/3/7/15/30-day schedule; practice prefers past/online questions and only uses AI-generated ones when none exist.",
  "上传图片/文件作答(可拖拽或粘贴)": "Upload an image/file as your answer (drag or paste)",
  "上传文件/图片(可拖拽或粘贴)": "Upload files/images (drag or paste)",
  "不需要联网搜索考试信息——名称只作为标题,相关信息以你上传的资料和补充说明为准。AI 会据此直接生成学习地图和计划。(练习题仍会正常出题/搜题)": "No web search for exam info — the name is just a title; the AI relies on your uploaded materials and notes to build the study map and plan. (Practice questions are still generated/searched as usual.)",
