  "你手动收藏的题和随手记的笔记都在这里。错题本里的题不会自动进来。AI 也能读到这些笔记。": "Questions you saved and your free notes live here. Mistake-book questions don't come in automatically. The AI can read these notes too.",
  "你每次录音/录像作答的录像和 AI 点评都存在这里,随时回看当时的状态,也可以重做。": "Every recorded answer and its AI feedback are kept here — revisit them anytime, or redo them.",
