  "只判分、不写入用户记录;用户原本的作答不受影响。": "Grades only, not written to the user's records; their original answer is untouched.",
  "可以只说要求(比如「我更擅长逻辑推理,请体现」),也可以拖拽/粘贴/上传文件让 AI 参考。留空则只根据最新做题数据刷新。": "You can just state requirements (e.g. \"I'm better at logical reasoning, please reflect that\"), or drag/paste/upload files for the AI to reference. Leave blank to refresh only from your latest practice data.",
  "听力题:点播放、听完再作答(AI 合成的原创听力,可反复播放)": "Listening: play, listen, then answer (AI-synthesized original audio, replayable)",
  "回放已叠加原配乐(录制时未收音,这是题目给的原曲)": "Playback has the original backing track overlaid (the recording had no audio; this is the given music)",
  "回看录像+AI点评,可重做": "Replay recordings + AI feedback, redoable",
  "在「追杀计划」里新建考试(选类型;只想学知识、不考试就选「只学习」)。建好后 AI 会先做认知自评,再让你在「补充资料」补充资料/回答问题(也可用浏览器扩展从网页采集——拖拽、粘贴都行)。": "Create an exam under \"Murder Plan\" (pick a type; choose \"Study only\" if you just want to learn). The AI first self-assesses, then lets you add materials / answer questions under \"Materials\" (or capture from web pages via the browser extension — drag & paste work too).",
  "在学习网站登录后,用扩展「手动采集」抓当前页;想自动/批量采集,就在「问问杀手」里让 AI 派任务,扩展会在后台执行。": "After logging into a study site, use the extension's \"Manual capture\" to grab the current page; for automatic/bulk capture, ask the AI in \"Ask Killer\" to dispatch a task and the extension runs it in the background.",
