  "有任何想法、疑问、调整需求,直接说就行。也可以问我这个网站怎么用,或让我去某个已登录的学习网站采集资料。": "Any ideas, questions, or changes — just say so. You can also ask how the site works, or have me collect from a study site you're logged into.",
  "有新功能/公告时提醒你(收件箱也会收到)": "Get notified about new features/announcements (also in your inbox)",
  "有资料没法上传(纸质书、老师口头强调、目标分数等),或想直接告诉 AI 的补充说明,写在这里。": "Materials you can't upload (print books, things the teacher stressed, target score, etc.), or notes you want to tell the AI directly — write them here.",
  "有资料没法上传(纸质书、老师口头强调、目标分数等),或想直接告诉 AI 的话,写在这里。": "Materials you can't upload (print books, things the teacher stressed, target score, etc.), or anything you want to tell the AI — write it here.",
  "有问题直接聊。它什么都能看、也能帮你改,还能指挥浏览器扩展去网站采集。所有对话都能传文件、拖拽或粘贴截图。": "Just chat. It can see everything, make changes for you, and dispatch the browser extension to collect from sites. Every chat supports files, drag & paste screenshots.",
  "本题录像不开麦克风、不收声（这样外放的音乐才不会被手机掐掉、你才能听见）；评分只看画面并对齐所给音乐,不分析录到的声音。": "This video records with the mic OFF (so speaker music isn't cut off and you can hear it); grading looks only at the picture and aligns to the given music, not the recorded sound.",
