  "现在按「考试蓝图」组卷:先规划这门正式考试该考什么、各知识点出几道、总分多少,再据此组卷(题库不够会即时生成,所以组卷可能稍慢)。": "The mock is now built from an \"exam blueprint\": it first plans what the real exam should cover, how many questions per topic, and the total marks, then builds accordingly (missing questions are generated on the fly, so it may be a bit slow).",
  "生成学习地图和计划": "Generate study map & plan",
  "用 Chrome 扩展,把已登录的学习网站内容采集进资料库,全程不接触你的密码。想让 AI 自动翻页/批量采集,直接去「问问杀手」里说,它会指挥这个扩展执行。": "Use the Chrome extension to capture content from study sites you're logged into — it never touches your password. For automatic paging/bulk capture, just ask in \"Ask Killer\" and it will dispatch the extension.",
  "用于题目设计或功能问题——比如无法录音、题目与选项对不上、显示错乱、按钮无效等。(如果是题目本身出错/答案不对/歧义,请用「题目有问题」。)提交后会把这道题的完整信息和你的作答/草稿/追问一起发给开发者。": "For question-design or functional issues — e.g. can't record, question/options mismatched, garbled display, buttons not working. (For a wrong question/answer/ambiguity, use \"Question has a problem\".) On submit, the full question plus your answer/scratchpad/discussion is sent to the developer.",
