  "这是你的私人 AI 备考助手。先花 10 秒了解一下,再开始。": "This is your personal AI exam-prep assistant. 10 seconds to get oriented, then dive in.",
  "第一步:给它资料": "Step 1: Give it materials",
  "在「资料」页上传大纲、教材、真题(PDF/Word/图片都行),或用浏览器扩展从网页采集。资料越全,AI 越靠谱。": "In Materials, upload the syllabus, textbook, past papers (PDF/Word/image), or capture from web pages with the browser extension. The fuller the materials, the more reliable the AI.",
