  "「学习」看 AI 讲知识点,「练习」做题即时批改,做错的自动进「错题本」按科学间隔重练。": "Study shows AI explanations; Practice grades you instantly; wrong answers go to Mistakes and come back on a spaced schedule.",
  "随时看进度": "Track progress anytime",
