  "用扩展把网页资料采进资料库,或让 agent 自动采集": "Use the extension to capture web pages, or let the agent auto-collect",
  "用 Chrome 扩展,把已登录的学习网站内容采集进资料库,甚至让 agent 自动翻页采集。全程不接触你的密码。": "Use the Chrome extension to capture content from study sites you're logged into — or let the agent auto-paginate. Your password is never touched.",
  "你的采集令牌": "Your capture token",
  "安装扩展后,把它粘贴进扩展设置。": "After installing the extension, paste this into its settings.",
  "三步开始": "Three steps to start",
  "向 Will 要「采集扩展」文件夹,在 Chrome 打开 chrome://extensions,开启开发者模式,点「加载已解压的扩展程序」选中它。": "Get the extension folder from Will, open chrome://extensions, turn on Developer mode, click 'Load unpacked' and select it.",
  "点扩展图标,填入本网站地址和上面的令牌(只需一次)。": "Click the extension icon, enter this site's URL and the token above (once).",
  "在学习网站登录后:用「手动采集」抓当前页,或切到「🤖 Agent 自动」填个目标让它自己翻页采集。": "After logging into the study site: use 'Collect this page' for the current page, or switch to '🤖 Agent' and give it a goal to auto-paginate.",
